It is heavily inspired by, and reimplements the Google Cloud project-bootstrap
approach from, the following Apache-2.0 projects by Jay Lee and the GAM-team
contributors:

  Got Your Back (GYB)  -  https://github.com/GAM-team/got-your-back
  GAM                  -  https://github.com/GAM-team/GAM

No source code was copied verbatim; the flow (project creation, API enablement,
service-account key minting, and the IAP-brands technique for OAuth clients) was
re-implemented in TypeScript. All credit for the original approach belongs to the
GYB/GAM authors.
